Centers/ARL, will continue to provide cyber and electronic warfare threat representation, and component and systems-
level performance analyses to inform prototype technology development, inform design decisions and reduce risks through
experimentation and T&E of the Army's priority C4ISR technologies.
FY 2027 Plans:
Will maintain and advance M&S threat representation, analytical methodologies and performance analysis tools to conduct
SLV analyses of Army C3 systems and technologies to include Army tactical network systems (e.g., network baseline), and C3
