Supports the costs associated with the OTC civilian workforce for operational testing in support of a subset of Army and DoW
acquisition programs, focusing on high priority requests.
FY 2027 Plans:
Continue to support the costs associated with the OTC civilian workforce for operational testing in support of a subset of Army and
DoW acquisition programs, focusing on high priority requests.
