modeling scenarios and models for the test/evaluation and analysis network communities; c.) update and enhance intelligence
models for existing simulations and Mission Command Information Systems (MCISs). Includes modernization and life cycle
management of CAA's suite of models, simulations, data management, and analytic tools.
