A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This funding line is a key enabler of the Army's development and modernization priorities in support of the H-60 Black Hawk helicopter. The program develops, tests,
qualifies, and integrates the next generation capability for integration and implementation to the H-60 fleet to increase combat capability and reduce cognitive workload.

