D. Acquisition Strategy
Digital Backbone and Airframe Enhancements for Launched Effects development/Non-Recurring Engineering (NRE) will be developed and qualified through an
Engineering Services contract with Lockheed Martin/Sikorsky (Prime Contractor) located in Stratford, Connecticut.

Main Rotor Blade Modernization - Work will be performed in Fort Worth, Texas utilizing the Aviation and Missile Technology Consortium (AMTC) Other Transaction
Authority (OTA) contract vehicle.

Blade Integrity - Work is anticipated to be conducted in Locust, North Carolina utilizing the Aviation and Missile Technology Consortium (AMTC) Other Transaction
Authority (OTA) contract vehicle.

Blackhawk Modernization - Work will be performed in Stratford, CT through existing contracts with Lockheed Martin/Sikorsky.




